    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can use this function instead of the  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1433598-createtexttounicodeinfo",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "  function whenyou do not need to create a Unicode mapping structure. You simplyspecify the text encoding of the source text. However, this methodis less efficient because the text encoding parameter must be resolvedinternally into a Unicode mapping. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You cannot specify a version of Unicode. The function usesa 16-bit form of Unicode as the default.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You pass a Unicode converter object returned from ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CreateTextToUnicodeInfoByEncoding",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " to thefunction  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1433517-convertfromtexttounicode",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " or  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1433483-convertfrompstringtounicode",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to identify the information to be used for the conversion. Thesetwo functions modify the contents of the Unicode converter object. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You pass a Unicode converter object returned from ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CreateTextToUnicodeInfoByEncoding",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " to thefunction  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1433518-truncatefortexttounicode",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to identify the information to be used to truncate the string. Thisfunction does not modify the contents of the Unicode converter object.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you are converting the text stream to Unicode as an intermediaryencoding, and then from Unicode to the final destination encoding,you use the function  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coreservices/1433522-createunicodetotextinfo",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to create a Unicode converter object for the second part of the process. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
